Key Match Events: The Celtics led by 10 after three and scored the first 11 points of the fourth quarter to push their advantage to 93-72.
Miscellaneous Highlights: Jalen Green had 27 points for the Rockets. They lost for the third time in four games.
Others: Kristaps Porzingis added 11 points with five rebounds in his return after missing four games with a sprained left ankle.
